{"tid":1450592,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場","createTime":"2019-08-11T17:44:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T17:59:15.000Z","uid":219967,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"8f77670686a199a1b8ca138bb7956101f36e884d","tid":1450592,"uid":219967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:44:26.000Z","msg":"一人一 狂洗連登post [時事台]<br />\n唔該你出一份力，肯出post，聽日就係人都知入機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n標題：「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場"},{"pid":"3283bb132255c7ae1c093a919b864c24ae94a755","tid":1450592,"uid":292661,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:44:58.000Z","msg":"推爆佢"},{"pid":"91c9632b20b07b7b8e4816b45d69cbb7b5a1af7b","tid":1450592,"uid":226569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:45:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"828946eb5f524d5abfcb04f142796b6955783178","tid":1450592,"uid":9824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:45:15.000Z","msg":"幫手推晒機場post 上熱門"},{"pid":"1523b76cb97072285ba368517a06066973f2b7c5","tid":1450592,"uid":264036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:45:23.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50de0af248b8fb4c2e2ad8d9aaa0fc8d3984ed71","tid":1450592,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:45:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190811/s00001/fa6b48acf177d08f33398333ffc5e847.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190811%2Fs00001%2F